        DirectoryEntryType enum indicating whether the object is a file or a directory

      • blocksize

        public final long blocksize
        Block size reported by server. This is present for compatibility with WebHDFS - in the case of Azure Data Lake store this is always 256MB.

      • replicationFactor

        public final int replicationFactor
        Replication Factor reported by server. This is present for compatibility with WebHDFS - in the case of Azure Data Lake store this is always reported as 1 - the Azure Data Lake store does appropriate replication on the server side to ensure durability.

      • aclBit

        public final boolean aclBit
        boolean indicating whether file has ACLs set on it.

      • expiryTime

        public final java.util.Date expiryTime
        Date+time at which the file expires, as UTC time. It is null if the file has no expiry. It is null for directories.

      • permission

        public final java.lang.String permission
        the unix-style permission string for this file or directory
